== 停产 ==
2009年6月，联想发布了ThinkPad T400s型笔记本电脑，T400s及T410s系列兼具传统T系列的主流高性能配置和X系列的轻薄特性，抑制了X300/X301系列的市场。为了明确产品线划分，避免产品在市场上自相残杀，联想决定在2010年底之前停产X300/X301系列笔记本电脑。<ref>{{cite web|title=联想ThinkPad将放弃X300系列笔记本|publisher=新浪数码|url=http://tech.sina.com.cn/n/2010-07-13/09094419497.shtml|accessdate=2010-07-13|archive-date=2010-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100717062957/http://tech.sina.com.cn/n/2010-07-13/09094419497.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 评论 ==
=== 与MacBook Air的竞争 ===

2008年1月15日，[[蘋果公司|蘋果公司]]发布了号称为“世界上最薄的笔记本电脑”<ref>{{cite web|title=Apple - MacBook Air|publisher=苹果公司|url=http://www.apple.com/macbookair/|accessdate=2008-04-14|archive-date=2008-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080417174958/http://www.apple.com/macbookair/|dead-url=no}}</ref>：[[MacBook_Air|MacBook Air]]。短短三天后，在1月18日的[[Gizmodo|Gizmodo]]網站上就泄露了联想ThinkPad X300即将发布的消息<ref>{{cite web|title=Ultralight Lenovo X300 Series Thinkpad Leaked|publisher=Gizmodo，Gawker Media|url=http://gizmodo.com/346797/ultralight-lenovo-x300-series-thinkpad-leaked|accessdate=2008-04-14|archive-date=2008-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080122064744/http://gizmodo.com/346797/ultralight-lenovo-x300-series-thinkpad-leaked|dead-url=no}}</ref>。由于MacBook Air和ThinkPad X300在规格上比较接近：13.3英寸LED背光屏幕、约3磅的重量、使用（或选用）固态硬盘、价格相当（在MacBook Air选用SSD硬盘的情况下）。它们的定位都是超轻薄便携笔记本电脑。这样两个产品难免成为竞争对手，导致互联网上存在大量的对比评测文章<ref>{{cite web|title=Lenovo X300 vs. Apple MacBook Air... Fight!|publisher=瘾科技，Weblogs, Inc.|url=http://www.engadget.com/2008/02/15/lenovo-x300-vs-apple-macbook-air/|accessdate=2008-04-14|archive-date=2008-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080408164732/http://www.engadget.com/2008/02/15/lenovo-x300-vs-apple-macbook-air/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Price May Be Steep, but Thin ThinkPad Has Abundant Features|publisher=华尔街日报|url=http://online.wsj.com/public/article/SB120355033462481317-98S0n3KaWakClghLZsE_VmnFKRw_20090220.html|accessdate=2008-04-14|archive-date=2008-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080331133403/http://online.wsj.com/public/article/SB120355033462481317-98S0n3KaWakClghLZsE_VmnFKRw_20090220.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2008年3月18日，联想在[[北京|北京]]举行了ThinkPad X300在中国大陆地区的发布会。在发布现场，联想集团副总裁[[仪晓辉|仪晓辉]]向观众介绍ThinkPad X300，提到其内建光驱，具有可更换可扩充电池，具有RJ-45以太网接口<ref>{{cite web|title=仪晓辉：X300是ThinkPad的里程碑|publisher=搜狐数码|url=http://digi.it.sohu.com/20080318/n255775073.shtml|accessdate=2008-04-14|archive-date=2008-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080404200138/http://digi.it.sohu.com/20080318/n255775073.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>，被认为是暗讽苹果公司的MacBook Air，犯了不应该讥笑竞争对手的大忌<ref>{{cite web|title=联想Thinkpad X300：仪晓辉的公关败笔|publisher=新华数码|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/it/2008-03/21/content_7831165.htm|accessdate=2008-04-14|archive-date=2008-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080325062352/http://news.xinhuanet.com/it/2008-03/21/content_7831165.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。3月下旬开始，联想开始投放网页广告，“The no-compromise, ultraportable, 13.3" widescreen notebook with an optional integrated DVD drive and 3 USB ports, starting at just 2.9 lb. Everything else is just hot air.”又一次将MacBook Air放在了竞争对手的位置<ref>{{cite web|title=Lenovo X300 ad takes the MacBook Air head-on|publisher=瘾科技，Weblogs, Inc.|url=http://www.engadget.com/2008/03/20/lenovo-x300-ad-takes-the-macbook-air-head-on/|accessdate=2008-04-14|archive-date=2008-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080417000105/http://www.engadget.com/2008/03/20/lenovo-x300-ad-takes-the-macbook-air-head-on/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 中美定价差别 ===
联想在ThinkPad X300北京发布会当日公布了在中国大陆地区的官方建议零售价<ref>{{cite web|title=联想发布ThinkPad X300 价格高于苹果Air|publisher=新浪科技|url=http://tech.sina.com.cn/it/2008-03-18/11012084592.shtml|accessdate=2008-04-14|archive-date=2008-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080322230428/http://tech.sina.com.cn/it/2008-03-18/11012084592.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>：
* 1GB内存，3芯电池，无DVD刻录机版本建议零售价[[人民币|人民币]]24999元；
* 2GB内存，6芯电池，内建DVD刻录机版本建议零售价34999元。
对比联想在美国市场的定价（与高配置版本的相当的面向美国市场的版本建议零售价约3000[[美元|美元]]，以当时的汇率计算，该产品中美价差万元以上），消费者纷纷质疑联想的定价策略<ref>{{cite web|title=X300“定价门”将了联想一军|publisher=南方都市报|url=http://it.southcn.com/itthink/content/2008-03/25/content_4361367.htm|accessdate=2008-04-14|archive-date=2008-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080509155042/http://it.southcn.com/itthink/content/2008-03/25/content_4361367.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。对定价差异，联想集团董事长[[杨元庆|杨元庆]]表示：“好产品就应该有高价格，如果定价太便宜，用户可能会觉得产品不好”<ref>{{cite web|title=杨元庆谈X300高价：便宜了大家会觉得产品不好|publisher=新浪科技|url=http://tech.sina.com.cn/it/2008-03-18/12102084760.shtml|accessdate=2008-04-15|archive-date=2008-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080329032221/http://tech.sina.com.cn/it/2008-03-18/12102084760.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。但是这个解释产生了更多负面影响，消费者抱怨他们被联想当了软柿子<ref>{{cite web|title=评论:联想把中国用户当“软柿子”|publisher=人民网 via cnBeta.com|url=http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/51944.htm|accessdate=2008-04-15|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080331041019/http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/51944.htm|archivedate=2008-03-31}}</ref>。

